An Indian-origin man was shot at in Atlanta, United States. The victim identified as Sameer Patel was shot in the head and his condition is stated to be critical. Patel was working in a department store. Two unidentified persons barged into the store and opened fire at Patel.After attacking Patel, the duo stole cash box and fled from the spot.The entire incident was caught on camera. Sameer's family has been sent a copy of the CCTV footage.Sameer is a native of Gujarat's Patan district.ALSO READ:Another Indian killed in US, businessman Harnish Patel shot dead near his home